- CHANGES IN VERSION 0.2

	* The main MCMC sampling algorithms efficiently implemented in C++.

	* Function "bmixt"         is added.
	* Function "summary.bmixt" is added.
	* Function "plot.bmixt"    is added.
	* Function "print.bmixt"   is added.
	
